---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '2026-03-31';
---
<Layout title="WinLog - Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for WinLog iOS app.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <a href="/en/apps/winlog" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">&larr; WinLog</a>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2 text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">WinLog - Success Diary</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-muted">
        <p>OpenClaw ("we", "us", "our") built WinLog as a free application. This page is used to inform users regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Information Collection and Use</h2>
        <p>WinLog does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data to external servers. The app operates entirely on your device.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>No personal information is collected</li>
          <li>No usage analytics or tracking</li>
          <li>No third-party analytics services</li>
          <li>No advertising identifiers</li>
          <li>No account or registration required</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Voice Input</h2>
        <p>WinLog uses Apple's on-device Speech Recognition to transcribe voice input. Voice data is processed locally on your device using Apple Speech framework and is not sent to any external server. We do not have access to your voice recordings or transcriptions.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Biometric Data</h2>
        <p>WinLog supports Face ID and Touch ID for app locking. Biometric data is managed entirely by iOS and is never accessible to the app. We do not collect, store, or process any biometric information.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
        <p>All diary entries, insights, and preferences are stored locally on your device. No cloud sync is used. Data never leaves your device.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>WinLog does not use any third-party services that collect data.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>WinLog does not collect any personal information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@mdk.guru" class="text-accent-purple hover:underline">support@mdk.guru</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
